data.description: Welcome to 8474 N 68th St!  New price and a brand new roof, flashing, ventilation.  With some cosmetic efforts, this home will shine. This Cape Cod overlooks a full acre+ of green space lined with mature trees.  Simple touches to this 4 bedroom will be well worth it.    As mentioned - 4 total bedrooms - 2 on the main floor and 2 on the upper level.  Living room is a nice size room with a warm gas fireplace.  Kitchen and dining rooms take you out to the 3 season room with views of the robust acreage.  Plenty of outdoor space to entertain or possibly expand.  Lower level features a cozy rec space.  Plenty of storage and nice sized 2.5 car garage.  Have a look!
